---
import MediaCenter from "../components/MediaCenter";
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Bridge + Composite — Media Center (Astro + React)</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" >
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="container">
      <section class="card">
        <h1 class="title">Bridge + Composite — Media Center</h1>
        <p class="sub">
          <strong>Bridge</strong>: separa a abstração (controles/Remotes) das implementações (dispositivos/Devices).<br/>
          <strong>Composite</strong>: organiza os dispositivos em árvore (ex.: Casa → Sala → TV).
        </p>
        <div class="row">
          <span class="badge">Astro + React</span>
          <span class="badge">TypeScript</span>
          <span class="badge">Padrões: Bridge & Composite</span>
        </div>
        <hr class="hr" />
        <MediaCenter client:load />
        <hr class="hr" />
        <p class="small">
          Onde estão os padrões? Bridge: <code class="code">src/components/patterns/bridge/*</code>.
          Composite: <code class="code">src/components/patterns/composite/*</code>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
